@startuml
title Build and Run Flow (Current Implementation Summary)
skinparam activityArrowColor #FB8C00
skinparam ArrowColor #FB8C00

start
:select profile (dev | fastdev | release);
:clean build/<profile> output directory;
:cargo +nightly build workspace\n(excluding mod cdylib crates);
:build mod crates with --features init_api;
:copy core_engine binary and symbols into build/<profile>;
:copy mod dynamic libraries into build/<profile>;
:copy mod assets into build/<profile>/assets/<mod>;
:prepare runtime library search paths in run script;
:launch build/<profile>/core_engine;
stop

note right
Flow reflects current scripts:
- build.sh / build.ps1
- run.sh / run.ps1
end note
@enduml
